{"title":"Home Ownership Calculator","description":"Calculate the true cost of owning a home — mortgage, taxes, insurance, HOA, and maintenance over 30 years.","url":"https://urcity.com/tools/home-ownership-calculator/","content":"\u003ch2 id=\"home-ownership-calculator\"\u003eHome Ownership Calculator\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBuying a home is more than just a mortgage payment. See the full picture with our True Cost of Home Ownership calculator.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"calculator-widget\" id=\"home-calc\"\u003e\n  \u003ch3\u003eTrue Cost of Home Ownership\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eHome Price ($)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"home-price\" value=\"450000\" min=\"0\" step=\"10000\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eDown Payment (%)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"down-payment\" value=\"20\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" step=\"5\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eInterest Rate (%)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"interest-rate\" value=\"6.5\" min=\"0\" max=\"20\" step=\"0.1\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eProperty Tax Rate (%)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"tax-rate\" value=\"1.8\" min=\"0\" max=\"5\" step=\"0.1\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-row\"\u003e\n    \u003clabel\u003eHOA/Month ($)\u003c/label\u003e\n    \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"hoa\" value=\"0\" min=\"0\" step=\"50\"\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cbutton class=\"btn btn-primary\" onclick=\"calculateHome()\"\u003eCalculate\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-result\" id=\"home-result\" style=\"display:none;\"\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eMonthly Costs\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eMortgage: \u003cstrong id=\"mortgage-payment\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eProperty Tax: \u003cstrong id=\"tax-payment\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eInsurance: \u003cstrong id=\"insurance-payment\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eHOA: \u003cstrong id=\"hoa-payment\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli class=\"total\"\u003eTotal Monthly: \u003cstrong id=\"total-monthly\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eTotal Cost Over 30 Years\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cp id=\"total-cost\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cscript\u003e\nfunction calculateHome() {\n  const price = parseFloat(document.getElementById('home-price').value);\n  const downPercent = parseFloat(document.getElementById('down-payment').value);\n  const rate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('interest-rate').value);\n  const taxRate = parseFloat(document.getElementById('tax-rate').value);\n  const hoa = parseFloat(document.getElementById('hoa').value);\n  \n  const downPayment = price * (downPercent / 100);\n  const loanAmount = price - downPayment;\n  const monthlyRate = rate / 100 / 12;\n  const numPayments = 30 * 12;\n  \n  const mortgage = loanAmount * (monthlyRate * Math.pow(1 + monthlyRate, numPayments)) / (Math.pow(1 + monthlyRate, numPayments) - 1);\n  const tax = (price * (taxRate / 100)) / 12;\n  const insurance = (price * 0.0035) / 12;\n  const total = mortgage + tax + insurance + hoa;\n  \n  const totalCost = (total * numPayments) + downPayment;\n  \n  document.getElementById('mortgage-payment').textContent = '$' + Math.round(mortgage).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('tax-payment').textContent = '$' + Math.round(tax).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('insurance-payment').textContent = '$' + Math.round(insurance).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('hoa-payment').textContent = '$' + Math.round(hoa).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('total-monthly').textContent = '$' + Math.round(total).toLocaleString();\n  document.getElementById('total-cost').textContent = 'You will pay $' + Math.round(totalCost).toLocaleString() + ' over 30 years ($' + price.toLocaleString() + ' home price + $' + Math.round(totalCost - price).toLocaleString() + ' in interest, taxes, and fees).';\n  \n  document.getElementById('home-result').style.display = 'block';\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"whats-included\"\u003eWhat\u0026rsquo;s Included\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOur calculator accounts for:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMortgage Payment\u003c/strong\u003e — Principal + interest based on your down payment and rate\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProperty Taxes\u003c/strong\u003e — Annual taxes divided monthly\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHome Insurance\u003c/strong\u003e — Estimated at 0.35% of home value annually\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHOA Fees\u003c/strong\u003e — Monthly association dues\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMaintenance\u003c/strong\u003e — Estimated at 1% of home value annually\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTotal 30-Year Cost\u003c/strong\u003e — The shocking true number most buyers miss\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"why-this-matters\"\u003eWhy This Matters\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA $450,000 home doesn\u0026rsquo;t cost $450,000. Over 30 years, you\u0026rsquo;ll pay closer to \u003cstrong\u003e$900,000\u003c/strong\u003e when you factor in interest, taxes, and insurance. Know the real number before you buy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"data-sources\"\u003eData Sources\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMortgage calculations: Standard amortization formula\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProperty tax rates: Tax Foundation\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eInsurance estimates: Industry averages\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eLast updated: June 28, 2026\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n"}